    dc:creator "Gustafsson, Daniel R.; Lei, Lujia; Chu, Xingzhi; Zou, Fasheng" ;
    dc:date "2020" ;
    dc:title "Review of Chinese species of the Oxylipeurus - complex (Phthiraptera: Philopteridae), with descriptions of two new genera and five new species" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3677763>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3677765>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3677721>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3677727>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3677779>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3677755>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3677723>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3677743>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3677771>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3677749> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3677763>
    dc:description "FIGURES 76–78. Male terminalia, ventral views. 76, Cataphractomimus impervius new species ex Lophophorus sclateri sclateri. 77, Cataphractomimus mirapelta new species ex Lophophorus lhuysii. 78, Cataphractomimus junae new species ex Tragopan temminckii." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3677763/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3677765>
    dc:description "FIGURES 79–81. Male terminalia, ventral views. 79, Reticulipeurus mesopelios (Nitzsch [in Giebel], 1866) ex Chrysolophus pictus. 80, Reticulipeurus robustus (Rudow, 1869) ex Lophura nycthemera. 81, Reticulipeurus reevesi (Clay, 1938) ex Syrmaticus reevesi." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3677765/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3677721>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–2. Cataphractomimus impervius new species ex Lophophorus sclateri sclateri. 1, male habitus, dorsal and ventral views. 2, female habitus, dorsal and ventral views." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3677721/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3677727>
    dc:description "FIGURES 7–8. Reticulipeurus robustus (Rudow, 1869) ex Lophura nycthemera. 7, male habitus, dorsal and ventral views. 8, female habitus, dorsal and ventral views. Abbreviations: mds = mandibular seta." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3677727/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3677779>
    dc:description "FIGURES 92–95. Male dorsal temporal chaetotaxy. 92, Cataphractomimus mirapelta new species ex Lophophorus lhuysii. 93, Reticulipeurus robustus (Rudow, 1869) ex Lophura nycthemera. 94, Megalipeurus sinensis new species ex Arborophila gingica. 95, Sinolipeurus tetraophasis (Clay, 1938) ex Tetraophasis obscurus. Reticulation, antennae, coni, nodi, and carinae omitted for clarity. Exact position and size of setae differ slightly among species in each genus. Abbreviations: mts1–5 = marginal temporal setae 1–5; os = ocular setae; pas = preantennal seta; pns = post-nodal seta; pos = pre-ocular seta; pts = posttemporal seta; s1–7 = sensilla 1–7. Figures drawn at different scales." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3677779/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3677755>
    dc:description "FIGURES 69–70. Female subgenital plates and terminalia, ventral views. 69, Cataphractomimus impervius new species ex Lophophorus sclateri sclateri. 70, Reticulipeurus mesopelios (Nitzsch [in Giebel], 1866) ex Chrysolophus amhearstiae. Abbreviation: LAVP = lateral accessory vulval plates." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3677755/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3677723>
    dc:description "FIGURES 3–4. Male habitus, dorsal and ventral views. 3, Cataphractomimus mirapelta new species ex Lophophorus lhuysii. 4, Cataphractomimus junae new species ex Tragopan temminckii. Abbreviations: IAB = Interior anterior bulge; ITP = intratergal plate.”" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3677723/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3677743>
    dc:description "FIGURES 21–24. Male antennae. 21, Cataphractomimus impervius new species ex Lophophorus sclateri sclateri. 22, Cataphractomimus mirapelta new species ex Lophophorus lhuysii. 23, Cataphractomimus junae new species ex Tragopan temminckii. 24, Reticulipeurus mesopelios (Nitzsch [in Giebel], 1866) ex Chrysolophus pictus. All figures drawn to same scale. Note that the pedicel of C. mirapelta is folded dorsally, and is longer than in the illustrated specimen." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3677743/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3677771>
    dc:description "FIGURE 88. Cataphractomimus impervius new species ex Lophophorus sclateri sclateri. Chaetotaxy of male legs, dorsal and ventral views. Abbreviations: a = anterior seta; b = sensilla basiconica; c = coxa; d = dorsal seta; dm = distal marginal seta; f = femur; p = posterior marginal seta; s = sensillus; sf = spiniform seta; spn = spine of the thumb-like process; t = trochanter; tb = tibia; th = tactile hair; tr = tarsi; v = ventral seta." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3677771/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3677749>
    dc:description "FIGURES 33–44. Male genitalia. 33–35, Cataphractomimus impervius new species ex Lophophorus sclateri sclateri. 33, genitalia, dorsal view. 34, paramere, dorsal view. 35, mesosome, ventral view. 36–38, Cataphractomimus mirapelta new species ex Lophophorus lhuysii Geoffroy. 36, genitalia, dorsal view. 37, paramere, dorsal view. 38, mesosome, ventral view. 39–41, Cataphractomimus junae new species ex Tragopan temminckii. 39, genitalia, dorsal view. 40, paramere, dorsal view. 41, mesosome, ventral view. 42–44, Reticulipeurus mesopelios (Nitzsch [in Giebel], 1866) ex Chrysolophus pictus. 42, genitalia, dorsal view. 43, paramere, dorsal view. 44, mesosome, ventral view. All figures drawn to same scale. Abbreviations: pst1–2 = parameral setae 1–2." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3677749/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

